## Summary
This documentation explains how to integrate OpenTelemetry distributed tracing with SuperTokens authentication APIs using the `@supertokens-plugins/opentelemetry-nodejs` plugin, which automatically instruments all overridable functions and APIs with spans following naming patterns like `<recipe-name>.function.<function-name>` and `<recipe-name>.api.<api-name>`.

